OL,3,CChildren may face up to 3-mile walk to
OL,4,Cschool as council proposes transport
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FSome schoolchildren in Caerphilly
OL,8,Fcould face a nearly three-mile walk to
OL,9,Fschool as the council looks at ways to
OL,10,Fsave money.
OL,12,FIt comes as Caerphilly County Borough
OL,13,FCouncil has proposed increasing the
OL,14,Fminimum distance that children must
OL,15,Flive away from school if they are to
OL,16,Fqualify for free transport.
OL,18,FIt's part of cost-cutting measures the
OL,19,Fcounty borough is looking into amid
OL,20,Fwhat it calls "significant financial
OL,21,Fchallenges".
