OL,3,CChildren may face up to 3-mile walk to
OL,4,Cschool as council proposes transport
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FCurrently, primary school pupils must
OL,8,Flive at least 1.5 miles away from
OL,9,Ftheir school to qualify, but this
OL,10,Fcould rise to two miles under the
OL,11,Fcouncil's new proposals.
OL,13,FSimilarly, secondary school pupils
OL,14,Fcurrently qualify for free transport
OL,15,Fif they live more than two miles away
OL,16,Ffrom their school, but this could now
OL,17,Frise to three miles.
