OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FThe council has said it will listen to
OL,8,Fthe public before making any changes,
OL,9,Fbut a local Senedd member has called
OL,10,Fthe proposals a "retrograde step"
OL,11,Fwhich could jeopardise some children's
OL,12,Fhopes of attending a Welsh-language
OL,13,Fschool.
OL,15,FThis week it emerged the council had
OL,16,Fspent an extra #1.4 million on school
OL,17,Ftransport last year than originally
OL,18,Fbudgeted.
