OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FAt a cabinet meeting on Wednesday July
OL,8,F17, members heard that the council was
OL,9,F"looking at starting discussions at
OL,10,Fsome point in the future" about making
OL,11,Fchanges to the current school
OL,12,Ftransport rules as an "opportunity for
OL,13,Fa saving".
OL,15,FThe cuts to school transport services
OL,16,Fcould save around #1.5m a year, the
OL,17,Fcouncil has said.
