OL,4,Cschool as council proposes transport
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FThe council has confirmed that
OL,8,Ftransport provision for children with
OL,9,Fadditional learning needs, or who are
OL,10,Funder the statutory school age or in
OL,11,Fpost-16 education, will not be
OL,12,Faffected.
OL,14,F"The council's transport budget is
OL,15,Funder significant financial pressure
OL,16,Fand we are one of the last councils in
OL,17,FWales to offer a more generous
OL,18,Fdiscretionary mileage policy," a
OL,19,Fcouncil spokesperson said.
