OL,3,CChildren may face up to 3-mile walk to
OL,4,Cschool as council proposes transport
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FHe claimed the proposals are
OL,8,F"particularly damaging for families
OL,9,Fwithout a car" and says the changes
OL,10,F"may also mean children will not be
OL,11,Fable to start or continue education in
OL,12,Fa Welsh medium setting due to the
OL,13,Fnature of such schools having a larger
OL,14,Fcatchment area, meaning they are often
OL,15,Fnot the 'local' school for many of
OL,16,Ftheir pupils".
OL,18,FSuch a move could lead to the council
OL,19,F"undermining" the Welsh Government's
OL,20,Fplans for one million Welsh speakers,
OL,21,FMr Owen Griffiths said.
